itunes:title: FEB 08 2022 - TRUCKERS SHUT DOWN BRIDGE BETWEEN DETROIT AND CANADA
title: FEB 08 2022 - TRUCKERS SHUT DOWN BRIDGE BETWEEN DETROIT AND CANADA
description:
Canadian truckers have officially blocked traffic in the largest suspension bridge between Detroit and Canada with their protest, meanwhile President Macron has met with President Putin to discuss a possible Russian invasion of Ukraine; after a frenetic diplomatic weekend at the Olympics, China has welcomed Argentina into its global belt initiative, and Jill Biden admits that the 2 free years of community college has been removed from President Biden’s ‘Build Back Better’ bill. 


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
